      "name": "Smishing Triad / Panda Shop",
      "description": "Chinese-speaking cybercriminal group operating a Phishing-as-a-Service (PhaaS) platform specializing in SMS phishing (smishing). Known for mass domain registration and rapid infrastructure churn. Previously linked to 194,000+ malicious domains globally.",
