      "modified": "2026-04-27T23:00:00.000Z",
      "name": "Panda Shop Korea Smishing April 2026",
      "description": "Coordinated smishing campaign targeting Korean users via 8 domains registered through Dynadot between 2026-04-19 and 2026-04-23. Domains impersonate delivery services, government notices, Apple, and document viewers. All hosted on 152.32.243.224 (UCloud Korea, AS135377). Server employs anti-analysis IP filtering returning HTTP 403 to researcher IPs.",
      "first_seen": "2026-04-19T00:00:00.000Z",
      "last_seen": "2026-04-27T23:00:00.000Z"
    },
