      "name": "Panda Shop Korea Phishing Server",
      "description": "Ubuntu Linux server running Node.js-based phishing kit on port 80 with OpenSSH 8.9p1 on port 2202. Hosted on UCloud Korea (AS135377). Implements IP-based access control to block security researchers.",
